      "title": "Reception at Nadunisi: Meet at noon",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Several prominent MPs of the Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna gathered together at midnight last night to welcome former President Gotabaya Rajapaksa on his arrival at the Katunayake Airport.",
        "Also, it has been reported that many important dignitaries have visited Gotabaya's house in Malalasekara Mawatti, Colombo since noon today."
      ],
